Pterostilbene Promotes Mean Lifespan in Both Male and Female Drosophila 
Melanogaster Modulating Different Proteins in the Two Sexes.

Beghelli D(1), Zallocco L(2), Barbalace MC(3), Paglia S(4), Strocchi S(5), 
