L(6), Angeloni C(3).

Author information:
(1)School of Biosciences and Veterinary Medicine, University of Camerino, Via 
Gentile III da Varano, 62032 Camerino (MC), Italy.
(2)Department of Pharmacy, University of Pisa, 56126 Pisa, Italy.
(3)Department for Life Quality Studies, Alma Mater Studiorum, University of 
